Package: bcadata
Title: Data Package for Business Cycle Anatomy
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "DeHaven", , "matthew_dehaven@brown.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Data package to recreate the data used in the paper, "Business Cycle Anatomy", by Angeletos, Colard, and Dellas (2020).  Creates 10 macro time series that can be used to match their VARs.
